data.description: If outdoor spaces and natural light is your thing. This two bedroom two bath house is your next home. Morning and evening outdoor time is no problem with patio areas on the East and West side of this home. The main living area and the dining area both have large picture windows and the nature light flows in. The ample dining room also has a built in display cabinet. The kitchen area is stunning with glass door uppers a tile back splash and a stainless vent over the stove. The main bedroom also has good lighting and a door to the back sitting area. The back yard is secluded and has a brick and block fence. The main bathroom has an oversize updated shower a vanity with dual sinks and a couple rows of glass blocks by the vanity to follow the theme of natural light. The second bedroom is good sized with ample closet area. The main hallway through the home is lined with extra storage. Come have a look, you will not be disappointed.
